 "Title":"Establishes the \"SNAP for students act\"",
 "Summary":"Establishes the \"SNAP for students act\" requiring the office of temporary and disability assistance to create informational materials to provide information regarding student eligibility for SNAP benefits and to provide digital versions of such materials to institutions of higher education in the state; requires institutions of higher education to notify students of their potential eligibility for SNAP benefits.",
